## §8. RISK ASSESSMENT

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Threshold values wrong (baseline guess) | Ship Phase 1, calibrate Phase 2 |
| Swarm storm (survival critical → 11 cells swarm) | downgradeLevelForSwarm() reduce by 1 tier |
| getTotalSignal() expensive (O(n) every 5s) | n < 50 signals typical, negligible |
| BackPressureGuard emit create feedback loop | EventBus idempotency check prevents |
| QuantumBuffer emit on every getQueueLength() call | Rate limit or debounce if called > 10/s |

